# Example Environment Variables

Copy these files and fill in your actual values.

## server/.env.example
```env
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/database
MQTT_BROKER_URL=mqtts://your-broker.hivemq.cloud:8883
MQTT_USERNAME=your_mqtt_username
MQTT_PASSWORD=your_mqtt_password
MQTT_TOPIC=esp32/health/data
MQTT_PORT=8883
PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=development
```

## client/.env.example
```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:3001
VITE_USER_ID=user1
VITE_USER_NAME=User 1
```

## Setup Instructions

1. Copy example files:
```bash
# Server
cp server/.env.example server/.env

# Client
cp client/.env.example client/.env
```

2. Fill in your actual credentials in the `.env` files
3. Never commit `.env` files (they're in `.gitignore`)
